ers include the actor  Jack Nicholson  (  b. 1937 ) and the golfer  Jack Nicklaus  (  b. 1940 ).  See also  Jock    and   Jake ."]}]},{"name":"II","type":"FIRST","attribution":"Dictionary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["‘Loving’."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Jaczo II von Gützkow was born about 1244, in Salzwedel, Altmarkkreis Salzwedel, Saxony-Anhalt, Germany as the son of Johann I von Gützkow and Unknown. He had at least 1 daughter with Cacislawa von Putbus. He died about 1303, in Germany, at the age of 61."},"et":{"about 1244–about 1303":"umbes 1244–umbes 1303","1244–1303":"1244–1303","1247–1295":"1247–1295","1259–1334":"1259–1334","1227–1264":"1227–1264","–Female":"Surnud","1264":"1264","1295":"1295","1227":"1227","1259":"1259","1303":"1303","1247":"1247","1334":"1334","about 1259":"umbes 1259","about 1303":"umbes 1303","1244":"1244","about 1244":"umbes 1244","about 1264":"umbes 1264","about 1295":"umbes 1295","Salzwedel, Altmarkkreis Salzwedel, Saxony-Anhalt, Germany":"Salzwedel, Altmarkkreis Salzwedel, Sachsen-Anhalt, Saksamaa","Germany":"Saksamaa"},"fi":{"about 1244–about 1303":"noin 1244–noin 1303","1244–1303":"1244–1303","1247–1295":"1247–1295","1259–1334":"1259–1334","1227–1264":"1227–1264","–Female":"Kuollut","1264":"1264","1295":"1295","1227":"1227","1259":"1259","1303":"1303","1247":"1247","1334":"1334","about 1259":"noin 1259","about 1303":"noin 1303","1244":"1244","about 1244":"noin 1244","about 1264":"noin 1264","about 1295":"noin 1295","Salzwedel, Altmarkkreis Salzwedel, Saxony-Anhalt, Germany":"Salzwedel, Altmarkkreis Salzwedel, Sachsen-Anhalt, Saksa","Germany":"Saksa"},"fr":{"about 1244–about 1303":"environ 1244–environ 1303","1244–1303":"1244–1303","1247–1295":"1247–1295","1259–1334":"1259–1334","1227–1264":"1227–1264","–Female":"Décédée","1264":"1264","1295":"1295","1227":"1227","1259":"1259","1303":"1303","1247":"1247","1334":"1334","about 1259":"environ 1259","about 1303":"environ 1303","1244